AMENDEDANALYSIS
Thisbill:
I. Directs electric distribution utilities to make available alternative tariffs for net metering to
eligible customer-generators in accordance with PUC Order 26,029 and net metering rules adopted
bythecommission.
II. Authorizes energy storage in connection with net metering and directs the department of
energytoadoptrulesrelativetotheinstallationandinterconnectionofsuchenergystoragesystems.
